  "texts": [
    "As a result, we have again from (7) that σ 2 i (Φ) + σ 2 i (Ω) = 1 for i ∈ {1, 2,.",
    "The proof is thus completed.",
    "Suppose that P and Q are m × m diagonal matrices, and their diagonal entries are non-negative.",
    "Let S be a PD matrix of m × m with smallest eigenvalue λ min, then we have that Tr(PSQ) ≥ λ min Tr(PQ).",
    "Let p i and q i be the (i, i)-th entry of P and Q, respectively."
  ]
